<html xmlns:o='urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office' xmlns:w='urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word'><head><meta charset='utf-8'><title>IELTS Answers</title></head><body><h1>DAILY ROUTINE ANSWERS</h1><h3>Câu 1: Can you tell me about your typical morning routine?</h3><p><strong>Trả lời:</strong> get dressed, take on clothes.<br>do my room, do excericise -> check on phone for new messages, notifications -> go to school. <br>What do you have for your breakfast ?.<br>Have you ever cooked ?<br>Do you love cooking ?. -> fried egg and omlette. <br>mineral water or an orange juice, smoothies for a drink. <br><br><br><br><br><br><br> </p><hr><h3>Câu 3: Do you like going out for a short walk?</h3><p><strong>Trả lời:</strong> get dressed, take on clothes.<br>do my room, do excericise -> check on phone for new messages, notifications -> go to school. <br>What do you have for your breakfast ?.<br>Have you ever cooked ?<br>Do you love cooking ?. -> fried egg and omlette. <br>mineral water or an orange juice, smoothies for a drink. <br>1. heat (v) the pan -> làm nóng chảo.<br>2. pour the oil into the pan. <br>3. break the egg shells and stir (v): khuấy it with a pin (thìa) of salt and peper.<br>4. pour the mixture into the pan and wait 2 minutues. <br>5. The dish is ready to serve/ Let's enjoy the dish.<br>-> How to make smoothies ?.<br>1. First, i go to convinient store to buy ingredients (nguyên liệu).<br>-> I have some fruits, a can of milk, ... <br>->I wash the fruit skin, peel the skins  and cut into smaller pieces<br>-> put the fruits, milk and some ice cubes into the Blender. <br>-> turn on the button and wait 2 minutues <br>5. The dish is ready to serve/ Let's enjoy the dish.<br>Do you like going out for a short walk ?<br>-> Yes, absolutely. <br>-> maintain body fitness. (lợi ích physical). (health) -> Only 30 minutes for walking a day to boost your health -> avoid overweight, blood pressure, .... <br>-> relax (entertainment) afer school<br>-> prefer to go with friend (exchange small convesations)<br>Where do you go for a short walk ?.<br>park -> why ? ->  walkpath is large and not crowded (đông nghẹt).<br>What do you do at the park ?.<br>At the evening, i do some excercise. There are many excercise equipment publiced to practise, sometimes i also meet up and goosip with my friends. We sit on the chair under the shade of the tree. It is very cool.<br>What does the park look like ?<br>There are a garden with flowers, sands, lakes, trees, chairs, bends, swing and slide.  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br> </p><hr><h3>Câu 6: Do you like going shopping?</h3><p><strong>Trả lời:</strong> Do you like going shopping?<br>a slave of fashion, ...<br>Where do you usually go shopping ?. <br>convinient store, grocery, suppermarket, mall, ... <br>Which one do you prefer to go shopping ? <br><br><br><br><br><br><br></p><hr><h3>Câu 7: What do you usually buy and where do you go?</h3><p><strong>Trả lời:</strong> Do you like going shopping?<br>a slave of fashion, ...<br>Where do you usually go shopping ?. <br>convinient store, grocery, suppermarket, mall, ... <br>Which one do you prefer to go shopping ? <br>-> Supermarket, mall. (full merchanises, more options to offer, have air conditions, entertainment, have better security, parking, every items have price tags on it, so you do not have to bargain...)   <br>-> Traditional market (cheaper, fresh).<br><br><br><br><br><br><br></p><hr><h3>Câu 8: When and Why do you go shopping?</h3><p><strong>Trả lời:</strong> Do you like going shopping?<br>a slave of fashion, ...<br>Where do you usually go shopping ?. <br>convinient store, grocery, suppermarket, mall, ... <br>Which one do you prefer to go shopping ? <br>-> Supermarket, mall. (full merchanises, more options to offer, have air conditions, entertainment, have better security, parking, every items have price tags on it, so you do not have to bargain...)   <br>-> Traditional market (cheaper, fresh).<br>Have many special discount, coupons (mã giảm giá) -> 15%, 20%.<br>-> frugal (adj): tiết kiệm.<br>-> ____.<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br></p><hr><h3>Câu 9: Do you like going out for a drink or eating out?</h3><p><strong>Trả lời:</strong> -> địa điểm nào -> địa điểm có gì -> là khu vực để nói chuyện với bạn -> tạo kỉ niệm, vui vẻ.<br></p><hr><h3>Câu 10: Where and When do you usually meet your friends?</h3><p><strong>Trả lời:</strong> -> lecture hall, library -> we are classmates. <br></p><hr><h3>Câu 12: Do you like watching TV or going to the gym?</h3><p><strong>Trả lời:</strong> What is your favourite show ?<br>My favourite show is Conan, _detective film, it decribes the journey of main charactor, Conan who is very intelligient. He is turned into a kid by accidient/crime (tội ác). He solves many crimes to return back to normal.   <br>Do you prefer to watch TV or go to the gym ?.<br>I am more into the gym. health concious (ý thức) kind of person.<br></p><hr></body></html>